{{TennisEventInfo|1976|Monte Carlo WCT| | date= 13 – 20 April | edition=71st | category=[[World Championship Tennis]] (WCT) | prize_money=$60,000 | draw=16S/8D | surface=[[Clay court|Clay]] / outdoor | location=[[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]] | venue=[[Monte Carlo Country Club]] | champms={{flagicon|ARG}} [[Guillermo Vilas]] <ref name="ms">{{cite web|title=1976 Monte Carlo WCT Men's Singles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/monte-carlo/410/1976/draws?matchType=singles|website=www.atpworldtour.com|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref> | champws={{flagicon|FRG}} [[Helga Masthoff]] | champmd={{flagicon|FRG}} [[Karl Meiler]] / {{flagicon|POL}} [[Wojciech Fibak]] <ref name=md>{{cite web|title=ATP – 1976 Monte Carlo WCT Men's Doubles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/Share/Event-Draws.aspx?Year=1976&EventId=410&Draw=md|publisher=ATP}}</ref> | champwd={{flagicon|FRG}} [[Katja Ebbinghaus]] / {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Helga Masthoff]]
| main_name=Monte Carlo Open{{!}}Monte Carlo WCT }}
The '''1976 Monte Carlo WCT''' was a combined men's and women's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]] at the [[Monte Carlo Country Club]] in [[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]]. The men's tournament was part of the [[World Championship Tennis]] (WCT) tour. It was the 71st edition of the event and was held from 13 April through 20 April 1976. [[Guillermo Vilas]] and [[Helga Masthoff]] won the singles titles.<ref name=wot1977>{{cite book|title=World of Tennis 1977 : a BP yearbook|year=1977|publisher=Macdonald and Janes|location=London|isbn=9780354090117|pages=146,165|editor=[[John Barrett (tennis)|John Barrett]]}}</ref>
==Champions== ===Men's Singles=== {{flagicon|ARG}} '''[[Guillermo Vilas]]''' defeated {{flagicon|POL}} [[Wojciech Fibak]] 6–1, 6-1, 6–4
===Women's Singles=== {{flagicon|FRG}} '''[[Helga Masthoff]]''' defeated {{flagicon|URU}} [[Fiorella Bonicelli]] 6–4, 6-2
===Men's Doubles=== {{flagicon|FRG}} '''[[Karl Meiler]] / {{flagicon|POL}} [[Wojciech Fibak]]''' defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Björn Borg]] / {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Guillermo Vilas]] 7–6, 6–1
===Women's Doubles=== {{flagicon|FRG}} '''[[Katja Ebbinghaus]] / {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Helga Masthoff]]''' defeated {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Rosie Reyes|Rosie Reyes Darmon]] / {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Gail Sherriff|Gail Lovera]] 6–3, 7–5
