The '''''British Bechuanaland Government Gazette''''' was the [[government gazette]] of [[British Bechuanaland]]. It was published between 1887 and 1895,<ref name="Walker1963">{{cite book|last=Walker|first=Eric Anderson|title=The Cambridge History of the British Empire|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ISg9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA909|year=1963|publisher=CUP Archive|page=909|id=GGKEY:J4RZC934KC3}}</ref> after which British Bechuanaland became part of [[Cape Colony]]. It was replaced by the ''[[Cape of Good Hope Government Gazette]]''.

