Kolegjet profesionale, private "Medicom", is a defunct [[Higher Education]] institution (HEI) in [[Tirana]], [[Albania]]. On 6 August 2014 its licence was permanently revoked by the [[Albanian Ministry of Education and Sports]] (MAS),<ref>[http://www.arsimi.gov.al/ "Ministria e Arsimit dhe Sportit"]</ref> through decision no. 539 of the [[Cabinet of Albania|Albanian Council of Ministers]], for not fulfilling the minimum legal requirements of higher education.<ref>Këshilli i Ministrave. [http://www.arsimi.gov.al/files/userfiles/arsimilarte/VKM/VKM_per_heqjen_e_licences.pdf "Për heqjen e licencës disa institucioneve private të arsimit të lartë"], Tirana, 6 August 2014. Retrieved on 7 December 2014</ref>

