[[File:Platin(duo).jpg|thumb|right|200px|Platin during a concert]]

'''Platin''' is a [[Slovenia]]n duo consisting of married couple Simon Platin and Diana Platin. They are best known for representing [[Slovenia]] at the [[Eurovision Song Contest 2004]] in [[Istanbul]], [[Turkey]] where they failed to advance to the final.

